-- This template returns the rate of customer who complete a Checkout session
select
  date_trunc('week', created) as week,
  1.0 * count_if(status = 'complete') / count(*) as conversion
from
  checkout_sessions
where
  date_trunc('week', created) >= date '2024-01-01'
group by
  1
<img src="https://editors-cdn.template.net/efc0b40f465208-44830ba8-b515-4d42-a3ef-0e6ef617d100.png" width="620"><h1>Executive Summary</h1><p>VIVIA Rentals is a new, technology-driven property management service founded by Jenny Rosen. The company is positioned to modernize the rental experience for property owners by leveraging automation and strategic marketing to maximize occupancy, streamline operations, and enhance profitability.</p><h2>Business Overview</h2><p>VIVIA Rentals provides a comprehensive, tech-forward management solution for residential rental properties. The core mission is to reduce owner workload and vacancy periods through a systematic, data-informed approach.</p><h3>Founder &amp; Vision</h3><p>Jenny Rosen is establishing VIVIA Rentals with a clear vision to bridge the gap between traditional property management and modern technological efficiency. The focus is on delivering reliable, high-touch service powered by intelligent systems.</p><h3>Core Service Model</h3><ul><li><p><strong>Structured Lease Terms:</strong> Offering flexible lease durations from 6 months to 2 years to cater to various tenant needs and market conditions.</p></li><li><p><strong>Diverse Property Types:</strong> Capable of managing a range of residential properties, including single-family homes, condos, and multi-unit buildings.</p></li><li><p><strong>Full-Service Management:</strong> Handling all aspects from tenant placement to maintenance coordination and financial reporting.</p></li></ul><h2>Strategic Advantages</h2><p>VIVIA's competitive edge is built on two proprietary, technology-centric systems designed to optimize the rental lifecycle.</p><img src="https://editors-cdn.template.net/f5e58e9c92a5b-4656b30d-81a4-4a0c-b354-9372e5a2dcb2.png" height="450"><h3>1. Automated Tenant Screening</h3><p>Utilizes advanced algorithms and data verification to efficiently and thoroughly qualify applicants. This process enhances tenant quality, reduces risk, and accelerates placement timelines.</p><h3>2. Multi-Platform Listing &amp; Lead Generation</h3><ul><li><p><strong>Syndicated Listings:</strong> Properties are automatically listed across major rental platforms to ensure maximum visibility.</p></li><li><p><strong>Live-Stream System:</strong> A proprietary method for generating qualified leads in real-time, dramatically increasing inquiry volume and speeding up the leasing process.</p></li></ul><h2>Expected Outcomes</h2><p>By integrating these strategic systems, VIVIA Rentals projects significant benefits for property owners.</p><h3>Maximized Financial Performance</h3><ul><li><p><strong>Higher Occupancy Rates:</strong> Reduced vacancy cycles through rapid, effective lead generation.</p></li><li><p><strong>Optimized Rental Revenue:</strong> Strategic pricing and qualified tenant placement protect and increase income streams.</p></li><li><p><strong>Operational Efficiency:</strong> Automation lowers administrative costs, improving net returns for owners.</p></li></ul><h3>Enhanced Owner Experience</h3><p>VIVIA's model is designed to provide peace of mind. Owners receive professional management, transparent communication, and detailed reporting, freeing them from day-to-day operational burdens.</p><h2>Conclusion</h2><p>VIVIA Rentals represents a modern, effective solution in the property management sector. By combining a structured service model with innovative technology for screening and marketing, the company is poised to deliver superior value, reliability, and financial results for residential property owners.</p>
